decl: theorem law_dual_dual {α} (l : MagmaLaw α) : l.dual.dual = l
og_raw:
theorem law_dual_dual {α} (l : MagmaLaw α) : l.dual.dual = l  := by
theorem law_dual_dual {α} (l : MagmaLaw α) : l.dual.dual = l := by simp [dual]
new_raw:
theorem law_dual_dual {α} (l : MagmaLaw α) : l.dual.dual = l   := by
  have lhs_dual_dual : l.lhs.dual.dual = l.lhs := by simp [FreeMagma.dual_dual]
  have rhs_dual_dual : l.rhs.dual.dual = l.rhs := by simp [FreeMagma.dual_dual]
  simp [dual, lhs_dual_dual, rhs_dual_dual]

decl:
theorem satisfiesPhi_dual {α G} [Magma G] {l : MagmaLaw α} {φ : α → G}
  (h : satisfiesPhi (Magma.opHom ∘ φ) l) : satisfiesPhi φ l.dual
og_raw:
theorem satisfiesPhi_dual {α G} [Magma G] {l : MagmaLaw α} {φ : α → G}
  (h : satisfiesPhi (Magma.opHom ∘ φ) l) : satisfiesPhi φ l.dual  := by
  simp only [satisfiesPhi, Op, opMagma, dual] at *
  rw [← evalInMagmaOp φ l.lhs.dual, ← evalInMagmaOp φ l.rhs.dual]
  simp only [Op, opMagma, dual_dual]
  exact h

decl:
theorem satisfiesPhi_dual {α G} [Magma G] {l : MagmaLaw α} {φ : α → G}
  (h : satisfiesPhi (Magma.opHom ∘ φ) l) : satisfiesPhi φ l.dual
og_raw:
theorem satisfiesPhi_dual {α G} [Magma G] {l : MagmaLaw α} {φ : α → G}
  (h : satisfiesPhi (Magma.opHom ∘ φ) l) : satisfiesPhi φ l.dual  := by
  simp only [satisfiesPhi, Op, opMagma, dual] at *
  rw [← evalInMagmaOp φ l.lhs.dual, ← evalInMagmaOp φ l.rhs.dual]
  simp only [Op, opMagma, dual_dual]
  exact h
new_raw:
theorem satisfiesPhi_dual {α G} [Magma G] {l : MagmaLaw α} {φ : α → G}
  (h : satisfiesPhi (Magma.opHom ∘ φ) l) : satisfiesPhi φ l.dual    := by
  simp only [satisfiesPhi, Op, opMagma, dual] at h ⊢
  have eq_dual_lhs := evalInMagmaOp φ l.lhs.dual
  have eq_dual_rhs := evalInMagmaOp φ l.rhs.dual
  have h₁ : evalInMagma φ l.lhs.dual = evalInMagma φ l.rhs.dual := by
    rw [← eq_dual_lhs, ← eq_dual_rhs]
    simp only [dual_dual]
    exact h
  exact h₁

decl: theorem implies_iff_dual {α} {l₁ l₂ : MagmaLaw α} : l₁.implies l₂ ↔ l₁.dual.implies l₂.dual
og_raw:
theorem implies_iff_dual {α} {l₁ l₂ : MagmaLaw α} : l₁.implies l₂ ↔ l₁.dual.implies l₂.dual  := by
  constructor
  · intro h G _ hsat
    exact satisfies_dual_dual (h (law_dual_dual l₁ ▸ satisfies_dual_dual hsat))
  · intro h G _ hsat
    rw [← law_dual_dual l₂]
    rw [← law_dual_dual l₁] at hsat
    exact satisfies_dual_dual (h (law_dual_dual l₁ ▸ satisfies_dual_dual hsat))
new_raw:
theorem implies_iff_dual {α} {l₁ l₂ : MagmaLaw α} : l₁.implies l₂ ↔ l₁.dual.implies l₂.dual   := by
  constructor
  · exact fun h G _ hsat => satisfies_dual_dual (h (law_dual_dual l₁ ▸ satisfies_dual_dual hsat))
  · exact fun h G _ hsat => law_dual_dual l₂ ▸ satisfies_dual_dual (h (satisfies_dual_dual (law_dual_dual l₁ ▸ hsat)))
